  <summary date="2021-12-14T20:58:54Z" status="Introduced in House">HOPE for HOMES Act of 2021

 This bill provides support for energy efficiency upgrades in homes.

 Specifically, the bill directs the Department of Energy (DOE) to establish a grant program that supports training on how to efficiently retrofit homes. In addition, DOE must establish a Home Energy Savings Retrofit Rebate Program to provide rebates for homeowners to invest in energy efficiency improvements.</summary>
